		<h1>Students</h1>
		<h3>These are some of our top picks for student quick dishes. They are have been divided into three different sections ,which can be found by following the appropriate link, they are breakfast, lunch, and dinner. Hope you enjoy and if you have any of your own recipes please send them to us our information can be found at the <a href="ContactUs.html">Contact Us</a> page.</h3>
		
